<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>- وَمَعْدُومٍ.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>- وَبِمَا لَا يَقْدِرُ عَلَى تَسْلِيمِهِ.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>-<span class="c5"> وَمَا حَدَثَ بَعْدَ الوَصِيَّةِ:</span> يَدْخُلُ فِيهَا.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>-<span class="c5"> وَتَبْطُلُ:</span> بِتَلَفِ مُعَيَّنٍ وُصِّيَ بِهِ.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>-<span class="c5"> وَإِنْ وَصَّى:</span><a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>-<span class="c5"> بِمِثْلِ نَصِيبِ وَارِثٍ مُعَيَّنٍ:</span> فَلَهُ مِثْلُهُ مَضْمُوماً إِلَى المَسْأَلَةِ.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>-<span class="c5"> وَبِمِثْلِ نَصِيبِ أَحَدِ وَرَثَتِهِ:</span> لَهُ مِثْلُ مَا لِأَقَلِّهِمْ.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>-<span class="c5"> وَبِسَهْمٍ مِنْ مَالِهِ:</span> لَهُ سُدُسٌ.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span>- وَبِشَيْءٍ، أَوْ حَظٍّ،<span class="c5"> أَوْ جُزْءٍ:</span> يُعْطِيهِ الوَارِثُ مَا شَاءَ.<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span>فَصْلٌ<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span>-<span class="c5"> وَيَصِحُّ الإِيصَاءُ إِلَى كُلِّ:</span><a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span><span class="c4">[١]</span> مُسْلِمٍ.<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span><span class="c4">[٢]</span> مُكَلَّفٍ.<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span><span class="c4">[٣]</span> رَشِيدٍ.<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span><span class="c4">[٤]</span> عَدْلٍ، وَلَوْ ظَاهِراً.<a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>